        "desc": "Si Trends lleva >4 semanas por encima de 30/100 y sigue creciendo, senal de entrada 60-90 dias antes del lanzamiento."
      },
      {
        "num": "02",
        "title": "Senal de Salida",
        "desc": "Si el hype explota en las ultimas 2 semanas (de 10 a 100), demasiado tarde para entrada PRE-lanzamiento."
      },
      {
        "num": "03",
        "title": "Empresa Optima",
        "desc": "Mid-cap, donde el juego represente >30% de ingresos futuros. Evitar gigantes donde el impacto queda diluido."
      },
      {
        "num": "04",
        "title": "Factor Cyberpunk",
        "desc": "Hype extremo + gap expectativas/realidad = crash. No confiar ciegamente en la aceleracion de Trends."
      }
    ],
    "en": [
      {
        "num": "01",
        "title": "Entry Rule",
        "desc": "If Trends has been above 30/100 for 4+ weeks and still growing, entry signal 60-90 days before launch."
      },
      {
        "num": "02",
        "title": "Exit Signal",
        "desc": "If hype explodes in last 2 weeks (10 to 100), too late for PRE-launch entry."
      },
      {
        "num": "03",
        "title": "Optimal Company",
        "desc": "Mid-cap, where the game represents >30% of future revenue. Avoid giants where impact is diluted."
      },
      {
        "num": "04",
        "title": "Cyberpunk Factor",
        "desc": "Extreme hype + expectations/reality gap = crash. Don't blindly trust Trends acceleration."
      }
